## Summary

This version is electrically compatible with earlier versions of G4 arenas. After a brief attempt to solve the electrical issues with higher voltages on the arena board and regulating it down on the comm boards, this version is a complete reimplementation of the G4 arena in KiCad.

We had two small production runs, both work well in our hands.

## Files

Additional files are in the `assets` folder. This includes the configuration for the autorouter, pdfs of the schematics, and photorealistic renderings of the PCB.

## Version

This board was developed as arena_12-12_v0.1. As this version number conflicts with several other development versions, we renamed it to v8. The different minor and patch versions stayed the same.

